  "texts": [
    "This system then facilitates communication from each group to their respective leaders and from leader to leader.",
    "Notably, the leader agent in this model is not considered a proxy, as it still directly interacts with the environment.",
    "Global controlIn this category, a globally shared communication policy is learned, providing more complete control over the communication links between agents.",
    "SchedNet [42] employs a global scheduler that limits the number of agents allowed to broadcast their messages, thereby reducing overall communication.",
    "FlowComm [92] learns a directed graph among agents, enabling unilateral or bilateral communication between them."
  ],
